This does not cover theft or damage caused by abuse or misuse. Product replacement or settlement (up to the limit of liability) will fulfill our obligation on your covered product. You can find more details in the Terms and Conditions below.

product.name: 13.3" Modern Black 3-Light Crystal Hallway Flush Mount Chandelier
product.shortDescription: This elegant flush mount-style ceiling light is further enhanced by a shining matte black finish, which complements the crystal accents. Illuminated within three bulbs, the various crystal droplets sparkle and shine with stunning brilliance.
product.description:
This elegant flush mount-style ceiling light is further enhanced by a shining matte black finish, which complements the crystal accents. Illuminated within three bulbs, the various crystal droplets sparkle and shine with stunning brilliance. Adorned with glittering crystal accents, this flush mount light is guaranteed to provide a dazzling accent. 

Features:

  • Modern-industrial style flushmount ceiling light 
  • Round clear crystal shade with an open bottom, allows for bulbs to be visible
  • Crystal Chandelier
  • Made of metal, crystal
  • Matte black fixture finish
  • Requires three E12 40 watts light bulbs (not included)
  • Dry safety rating
  • Flushed-Mount mounting
  • Dimmable
  • Hardwired power source
  • Voltage: 110 Volts
  • Room Use for Entry/ Foyer; Kitchen; Bedroom; Dining room
  • 1-year Limited Warranty

Dimensions:

  • Overall size: 13.3 inches Wide x 5.9 inches High
  • Overall Weight: 4.8 pounds
